Watch for patent races and shifts away from amyloid-focused therapies.","keyPoints":["Dva proteina kao okidač za uništenje neurona","Novi spoj razbija smrtonosni tandem — ali samo u glodavaca","Farma divovi već špijuniraju: tko ima patente?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/alzheimers-death-switch-the-mouse-study-hype-filte/main.jpg","alt":"Alzheimerov ‘prekidač smrti’: miševi su spaseni, ljudi čekaju"},"subtitle":"Između laboratorijske pobjede i kliničke realnosti leži 10 godina i milijarda dolara","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/alzheimers-death-switch-the-mouse-study-hype-filte/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Između laboratorijske pobjede i kliničke realnosti leži 10 godina i milijarda dolara"},"tags":["Alzheimer's Disease","Clinical Trials","Neurodegenerative Research"],"geo":{"name":"Menlo Park, CA","lat":37.4529,"lon":-122.1817,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$7","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-hyperagents-self-improving-ai-or-just-another-loop","title":"Hyperagenti: Samopoboljšavanje ili samo novi paket?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Novi [arXiv rad](https://arxiv.","execSummary":"This analysis cuts through the hype around 'hyperagents'—self-referential AI systems that merge task execution and self-improvement loops—by examining the Darwin-Gödel Machine's actual novel mechanism (recursive coding+evaluation) and its real-world viability. The piece contrasts the academic promise with deployment realities (cost, benchmark gaps) and maps competitive pressures on incumbent AI tooling vendors, while flagging the eerie silence around failure modes in open-ended improvement.","keyPoints":["Darwin-Gödelov stroj pokazuje otvoreno kodersko samopoboljšavanje","Hyperagenti kombiniraju zadatke i meta-poboljšavanje u jednoj petlji","Stvarni test: može li ovo raditi izvan kontroliranih benchmarkova?"],"source":{"name":"arXiv AI","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.19461"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/hyperagents-self-improving-ai-or-just-another-loop/main.jpg","alt":"Hyperagenti: Samopoboljšavanje ili samo novi paket?"},"subtitle":"Zašto bi ova matematička igračka mogla biti važnija od još jednog AI papira","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/hyperagents-self-improving-ai-or-just-another-loop/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Zašto bi ova matematička igračka mogla biti važnija od još jednog AI papira"},"tags":["Hyperagenti","Mathematical Modeling","Self-Improvement Algorithms"],"geo":{"name":"San Francisco, CA","lat":37.7749,"lon":-122.4194,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$8","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-jailbreaking-llms-when-optimization-turns-against-","title":"Automatsko lomljenje LLM-ova: tko je sljedeći na meti?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada se o sigurnosti velikih jezikovnih modela govori, većina proizvođača voli istaknuti brojeve poput 99% blokiranih štetnih upita ili nula uspješnih jailbreakova u testiranju.","execSummary":"New research exposes how adaptive, automated prompt optimization turns LLM safety benchmarks into a farce—demonstrating 40-60% jailbreak success rates where fixed tests show near-zero. The real story isn’t the vulnerability itself (which insiders already knew) but the **economic imbalance**: defense costs are spiraling while attack tools like DSPy democratize. Watch for silent shifts in enterprise security budgets and open-source red-teaming frameworks.","keyPoints":["Adaptivni napad na LLM-ove preko optimizacije upita","DSPy kao oruđe za automatizirano zaobilaženje sigurnosnih filtera","Benchmarkovi ne drže korak s realnim prijetnjama"],"source":{"name":"arXiv NLP","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.19247"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/jailbreaking-llms-when-optimization-turns-against-/main.jpg","alt":"Automatsko lomljenje LLM-ova: tko je sljedeći na meti?"},"subtitle":"Demo protiv deploymenta: zašto su fiksni testovi sigurnosti beskorisni","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/jailbreaking-llms-when-optimization-turns-against-/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Demo protiv deploymenta: zašto su fiksni testovi sigurnosti beskorisni"},"tags":["LLM","Deployment","Security Testing"],"geo":{"name":"Stanford, United States","lat":37.4275,"lon":-122.1697,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$9","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-23-when-solar-maintenance-cuts-your-output-by-5-6","title":"Čistači za solare koji ubijaju efikasnost: 5,6% gubitka?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-23T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Fraunhoferov CSP institut — onaj isti koji obično mjeri solarne module s njemačkom preciznošću — upravo je objavio neugodnu činjenicu: neka sredstva za čišćenje fotonaponskih panela ne čiste, nego kvare.","execSummary":"Fraunhofer CSP's findings expose a critical blind spot in solar PV maintenance: some cleaning agents permanently damage anti-reflective coatings, cutting efficiency by up to 5.6%. The real story isn’t the damage itself but the industry’s failure to standardize cleaning protocols—leaving end-users to bear the risk of voided warranties and performance losses. Watch for certification wars and legal pushback as manufacturers scramble to distance themselves from ‘unapproved’ products.","keyPoints":["Nekoliko sredstava za čišćenje tražno oštećuje antirefleksne premaz","Gubitak učinkovitosti do 5,6% — ali ne kod svih proizvoda","Proizvođači solarnih modula sada moraju revidirati preporuke"],"source":{"name":"PV Magazine","url":"https://www.pv-magazine.com/2026/03/23/fraunhofer-csp-warns-some-cleaning-agents-may-reduce-pv-module-performance-by-up-to-5-6/"},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/when-solar-maintenance-cuts-your-output-by-5-6/main.jpg","alt":"Čistači za solare koji ubijaju efikasnost: 5,6% gubitka?"},"subtitle":"Kada čistoća postane problem: tko je odgovoran za 5,6% manje struje?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/when-solar-maintenance-cuts-your-output-by-5-6/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Kada čistoća postane problem: tko je odgovoran za 5,6% manje struje?"},"tags":["Solar Panel Efficiency","Dust Accumulation","Renewable Energy Loss"],"geo":{"name":"Halle (Saale), Germany","lat":51.4826,"lon":11.9692,"countryCode":"DE"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$a","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-mangrovegs-when-80-accuracy-isn-t-enough","title":"AI predviđa metastaze: 80% točnosti ili samo novi hype?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada naučnici kažu da je pronađen „biološki program“ metastaza, odmah se čuje zvonjava alarmnih signala: je li ovo još jedan ai koji objašnjava rak kao „složenu, ali predvidivu“ igru, ili stvarno nešto novo.","execSummary":"MangroveGS claims 80% accuracy in predicting cancer metastasis across multiple types, but the real story is the 20% failure rate—and who bears the cost. Unlike most AI hype, this model offers a biological explanation, not just correlation, which could shift how oncologists make treatment decisions if validated. The catch? Clinical deployment is years away, and the developer community is already skeptical about reproducibility.","keyPoints":["Genetski 'program' raka otkriven u kolon tumorima","MangroveGS radi na više tipova raka – ali s 20% greške","Liječnici bi mogli manje agresivno liječiti – ako se potvrdi"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/mangrovegs-when-80-accuracy-isn-t-enough/main.jpg","alt":"AI predviđa metastaze: 80% točnosti ili samo novi hype?"},"subtitle":"Demo radi na 80%. Pitanje je tko će platiti cijenu pogreške","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/mangrovegs-when-80-accuracy-isn-t-enough/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Demo radi na 80%. Pitanje je tko će platiti cijenu pogreške"},"tags":["Cancer Diagnosis","Metastasis Prediction","Medical AI","Diagnostic Accuracy","Healthcare Technology"],"geo":{"name":"Boston, United States","lat":42.3601,"lon":-71.0589,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$b","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-22-nvidias-nemotron-cascade-2-smarter-or-just-smarter","title":"NVIDIA-ina igrica: 30B parametara, ali samo 3B aktivnih – što se tu stvarno događa?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-22T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"NVIDIA je upravo objavila [Nemotron-Cascade 2](https://www.","execSummary":"NVIDIA’s Nemotron-Cascade 2 frames 'intelligence density' as the next battleground—30B total parameters but only 3B active—yet the real play is ecosystem lock-in. The article dissects whether the benchmark hype (2025 ‘gold medal’) translates to real-world utility, who benefits (NVIDIA’s TensorRT users), and why open weights might be a trojan horse for proprietary infrastructure.","keyPoints":["MoE arhitektura sa 10× manjim aktivnim parametrima od konkurenata","Drugi otvoreni model s ‘zlatnom medaljom’ – ali koji benchmark to zapravo znači?","Agentičke sposobnosti ili samo bolje fine-tunanje za NVIDIA-ine alate?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/nvidias-nemotron-cascade-2-smarter-or-just-smarter/main.jpg","alt":"NVIDIA-ina igrica: 30B parametara, ali samo 3B aktivnih – što se tu stvarno događa?"},"subtitle":"Demo ili stvarnost: zašto je ‘inteligentna gustoća’ možda samo pametan marketing?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/nvidias-nemotron-cascade-2-smarter-or-just-smarter/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Demo ili stvarnost: zašto je ‘inteligentna gustoća’ možda samo pametan marketing?"},"tags":["NVIDIA","Large Language Models","AI Marketing"],"geo":{"name":"Santa Clara, United States","lat":37.3541,"lon":-121.9552,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$c","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-20-ai-s-self-improvement-problem-is-bigger-than-compu","title":"AI koji se sam unaprjeđuje: prekretnica ili još jedno obećanje?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Novi članak na arXivu pod šifrom [2603.","execSummary":"A new arXiv paper proposes a framework for 'continually self-improving AI', addressing three long-standing limitations of current models: inefficient learning from specialized data, reliance on human-generated datasets, and algorithmic constraints. While the theoretical approach is interesting, the lack of practical demonstrations and developer community engagement raises questions about its immediate impact. The real story here is not the promised innovation, but the persistent power imbalance in AI development – where those with access to large datasets and computing resources continue to dominate, leaving others struggling with inefficiencies.","keyPoints":["arXiv članak o samounaprjeđujućoj AI","Tri ključna ograničenja današnjih modela","Hype vs. realnost: tko zapravo profitira"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/ai-s-self-improvement-problem-is-bigger-than-compu/main.jpg","alt":"AI koji se sam unaprjeđuje: prekretnica ili još jedno obećanje?"},"subtitle":"Što se stvarno promijenilo – i zašto svi šute o pravom uskom grlu?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/ai-s-self-improvement-problem-is-bigger-than-compu/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Što se stvarno promijenilo – i zašto svi šute o pravom uskom grlu?"},"tags":["Self-Improving AI","AI Regulation","Multimodal AI"],"geo":{"name":"Mountain View, CA","lat":37.3861,"lon":-122.0839,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$d","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-20-autisms-nitric-oxide-link-a-real-signal-or-just-no","title":"Autizam i dušikov oksid: domino-efekt ili samo novi model?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kada znanstvenici kažu da su pronašli „molekularni okidač“ za nešto tako složeno kao autizam, prva reakcija bi trebala biti skepticizam — ne zbog same nauke, nego zbog istorije pretjerivanja u neuroznanosti.","execSummary":"The study links nitric oxide to mTOR pathway overactivation in some autism cases, but the real story isn’t the ‘domino effect’—it’s the narrow applicability and pharma’s potential to repurpose existing mTOR inhibitors. The hype overshadows the incremental (but real) progress: a mechanistic insight, not a cure.","keyPoints":["Dušikov oksid može osloboditi mTOR put u neuronima","TSC2 protein gubi „kočnicu“ pri povećanoj aktivnosti","Istraživanje otvara pitanja, ne donosi terapije"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/autisms-nitric-oxide-link-a-real-signal-or-just-no/main.jpg","alt":"Autizam i dušikov oksid: domino-efekt ili samo novi model?"},"subtitle":"Novi molekularni lanac ili samo elegantno objašnjenje za stari problem?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/autisms-nitric-oxide-link-a-real-signal-or-just-no/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Novi molekularni lanac ili samo elegantno objašnjenje za stari problem?"},"tags":["Autism","Nitric Oxide","Molecular Mechanism"],"geo":{"name":"Menlo Park, CA","lat":37.4529,"lon":-122.1817,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$e","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-20-qualcomms-arm-ambush-is-intels-laptop-crown-slippi","title":"Qualcomm peče Intel: ARM u Windowsu dobiva na težini?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-20T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Geekbench brojevi pokazuju istu priču: Qualcommov novi Snapdragon X2 Elite Extreme u ranim testovima nadilazi Intelov Core Ultra X9 388H iz nadolazeće Panther Lake obitelji.","execSummary":"Qualcomm's Snapdragon X2 Elite Extreme outperforms Intel's Panther Lake in early benchmarks, signaling ARM's growing threat to x86 in Windows laptops. The real question isn't raw speed but efficiency, developer adoption, and whether Intel's AI optimizations can offset Qualcomm's power advantages in real-world use.","keyPoints":["Snapdragon X2 Elite Extreme nadmašuje Intelov Panther Lake u Geekbench testovima","ARM arhitektura sve više ugrožava x86 dominaciju na Windows laptopovima","Kvalcommov potez stavlja pritisak na Intel da ubrza efikasnost, ne samo brutu snagu"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/qualcomms-arm-ambush-is-intels-laptop-crown-slippi/main.jpg","alt":"Qualcomm peče Intel: ARM u Windowsu dobiva na težini?"},"subtitle":"Rani benchmarkovi su lijepa priča — ali koliko to znači van laboratorija?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/qualcomms-arm-ambush-is-intels-laptop-crown-slippi/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Rani benchmarkovi su lijepa priča — ali koliko to znači van laboratorija?"},"tags":["Qualcomm","ARM","Benchmarking"],"geo":{"name":"San Diego, United States","lat":32.7157,"lon":-117.1611,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$f","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-19-transformers-finally-explained-it-was-bayesian-all","title":"Transformeri su Bayesovske mreže — ili paketiranje?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-19T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-19T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Ako vam je ikad bilo sumnjivo zašto transformeri dominiraju ai — sada postoji [formalni odgovor](https://arxiv.","execSummary":"A new arXiv paper proves transformers are mathematically equivalent to Bayesian networks, offering a formal explanation for their dominance—but the real question is whether this changes engineering practice or just retroactively justifies existing models. The gap between theory and deployment remains wide, with open-source communities and interpretability startups as the most likely beneficiaries.","keyPoints":["Jedna sloja transformera = jedna runda vjerojatnosnog zaključivanja","Dokaz vrijedi za nasumične, trenirane i konstruirane težine","Tko ovdje stječe prednost: teoretičari ili inženjeri?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/transformers-finally-explained-it-was-bayesian-all/main.jpg","alt":"Transformeri su Bayesovske mreže — ili paketiranje?"},"subtitle":"Matematički dokaz ili samo nova ambalaža za staru logiku?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/transformers-finally-explained-it-was-bayesian-all/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Matematički dokaz ili samo nova ambalaža za staru logiku?"},"tags":["Bayesian Networks","Transformers","Mathematical Proof"],"geo":{"name":"Menlo Park, CA","lat":37.4529,"lon":-122.1817,"countryCode":"US"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$10","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-17-roches-ai-factory-bet-blackwell-gpus-or-just-bigge","title":"Roche i NVIDIA: 3500 GPU-a ili samo novi omotač?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-17T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-17T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Roche je objavio globalno uvođenje 3.","execSummary":"Roche’s 3,500 Blackwell GPU deployment is framed as a breakthrough, but the real story is whether this is a scalable advantage or just a high-profile pilot. The article dissects the gap between NVIDIA’s benchmark claims and Roche’s actual integration challenges, while mapping who stands to gain—Roche, NVIDIA, or competitors watching from the sidelines.","keyPoints":["3500 Blackwell GPU-a u globalnom razmještanju — koliko je to stvarno?","Diagnostika i razvoj lijekova: gdje prestaje demo, a počinje stvarnost","Tko stječe prednost — Roche, NVIDIA ili konkurenti s manje buke?"],"source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/roches-ai-factory-bet-blackwell-gpus-or-just-bigge/main.jpg","alt":"Roche i NVIDIA: 3500 GPU-a ili samo novi omotač?"},"subtitle":"Kada je ’masovno skaliranje’ samo marketing, a kada stvarno ubrzanje?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/roches-ai-factory-bet-blackwell-gpus-or-just-bigge/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Kada je ’masovno skaliranje’ samo marketing, a kada stvarno ubrzanje?"},"tags":["Roche","NVIDIA","GPU Acceleration"],"geo":{"name":"Basel, Switzerland","lat":47.5596,"lon":7.5886,"countryCode":"XX"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$11","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-16-japan-s-agrivoltaic-reality-check-standards-over-h","title":"Japanske agrivoltaike: standardi ili spas za poljoprivredne paneliće?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-16T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-16T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"Kad se solarna energija i poljoprivreda susretnu pod istim krovom – doslovno – rezultati nisu uvijek sunčani.","source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/japan-s-agrivoltaic-reality-check-standards-over-h/main.jpg","alt":"Japanske agrivoltaike: standardi ili spas za poljoprivredne paneliće?"},"subtitle":"Kada 25% projekata donosi lošije prinose, regulatori reagiraju. Ali tko zapravo profitira?","subtitleImage":{"url":"/images/articles/japan-s-agrivoltaic-reality-check-standards-over-h/subtitle.jpg","alt":"Kada 25% projekata donosi lošije prinose, regulatori reagiraju. Ali tko zapravo profitira?"},"tags":["future-pulse","automated","ai"],"geo":{"name":"Japan","lat":36.204824,"lon":138.252924,"countryCode":"JP"},"featured":false,"approved":true,"content":"$12","lang":"hr"},{"id":"2026-03-16-physics-inspired-kernel-networks","title":"Yat-proizvod: Nov kernel ili samo pametno rebrandiranje?","category":"ai","date":"2026-03-16T12:00:00Z","scrapeDateDate":"2026-03-16T12:00:00Z","excerpt":"U svijetu strojnog učenja, gdje svaki tjedan dolazi novi 'revolucionarni' pristup, arXiv preprint arXiv:2603.","execSummary":"The paper introduces the 'yat-product', a kernel operator designed to replace conventional neural network blocks with a single geometrically-grounded operation. While mathematically elegant and showing promise in simplifying architectures, its real-world advantage remains unproven beyond controlled benchmarks. The key tension lies between theoretical innovation and practical adoption – will developers trade familiar pipelines for potentially more efficient but untested alternatives?","source":{"name":"","url":""},"image":{"url":"/images/articles/physics-inspired-kernel-networks/main.jpg","alt":"Yat-proizvod: Nov kernel ili samo pametno rebrandiranje?"},"subtitle":"Š